---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Menu from "../components/Menu.astro";
---

<Layout title="Convivencia | Ecosistema Humboldt">
  <main>
    <section class="max-w-[90%] md:max-w-[70%] mx-auto mt-28">
      <ul role="list" class="link-card-grid">
        <Menu
          href="copasst"
          title="Copasst"
          classes="py-2 px-3"
          targets="_self"
        />
        <Menu
          href="#convivencia"
          title="Comité de convivencia"
          classes="active py-2 px-3"
          targets="_self"
        />
        <Menu
          href="brigada"
          title="Brigadistas"
          classes="py-2 px-3"
          targets="_self"
        />
      </ul>
    </section>
    <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto">
      <span
        onclick="history.back()"
        class="text-azul-humboldt text-base mt-10 mb-3 block cursor-pointer"
      >
        <img src="img/volver.svg" alt="volver" width="20" class="inline mr-3" />
        Volver
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-black text-5xl mt-32 mb-3 font-bold">
        Comité de convivencia
      </h1>
    </div>

    <section class="mt-10" id="convivencia">
      <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div id="accordion-collapse" data-accordion="collapse">
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-1">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-1"
                aria-expanded="true"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-1"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  ¿Qué es el Comité de convivencia laboral?
                </span>
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-1"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-1"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <p class="mb-2 text-base">
                  Conjunto de personas que se encargan de recibir y dar trámite
                  a las quejas en las que se describan situaciones que puedan
                  constituir acoso laboral de acuerdo con lo definido en la Ley
                  1010 de 2006.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-2">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-2"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-2"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  Objetivo del Comité en el Instituto
                </span>
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-2"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-2"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <p class="mb-2 text-base">
                  Facilitar información a todos los trabajadores del Instituto
                  sobre la forma correcta de presentar una queja ante un
                  supuesto caso de acoso laboral y otros hostigamientos, de
                  forma que se pueda intervenir desde promoción y prevención
                  estas situaciones.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <h2 id="accordion-collapse-heading-3">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="flex items-center justify-between w-full p-5 border-b-2 gap-3"
                data-accordion-target="#accordion-collapse-body-3"
                aria-expanded="false"
                aria-controls="accordion-collapse-body-3"
              >
                <span class="text-base text-azul-light font-bold">
                  Documentos</span
                >
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class="w-3 h-3 rotate-180 shrink-0"
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                  fill="none"
                  viewBox="0 0 10 6"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke="currentColor"
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 5 5 1 1 5"></path>
                </svg>
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id="accordion-collapse-body-3"
              class="hidden"
              aria-labelledby="accordion-collapse-heading-3"
            >
              <div class="p-5">
                <p class="mb-2 text-base">
                  <a
                    href="docs/AGR-GH-R-01Reglamento-interno-de-trabajo.pdf"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Reglamento interno de trabajo</a
                  >
                </p>
                <p class="mb-2 text-base">
                  <a
                    href="docs/AGH-PL-02Politica-Para-la-prevencion-y-atencion-del-acoso-laboral-el-abuso-de-poder-con-fines-sexuales-y-la-discriminacion.pdf"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    >Politica para la prevención y atencion del acoso laboral,
                    el abuso de poder con fines sexuales y la discriminación</a
                  >
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="p-5">
              <p class="mb-2 text-base justify-self-center text-l">
                Contáctanos al correo <p
                  class="justify-self-center text-base text-azul-light font-bold text-xl"
                >
                  convivencia@humboldt.org.co
                </p>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h3 class="pl-5 text-base text-azul-light font-bold mb-8">
              Integrantes
            </h3>
            <p class="my-5 text-center font-bold">
              Representantes del empleador
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/viviana-quinceno.png"
                  alt="diana"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />

                <p class="text-center">Viviana Betancur Quiceno</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal-Presidente CCL</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/july.png"
                  alt="Isabel"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-center">July Hasbleidy Cubillos Leiton</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/erika-adelaida.png"
                  alt="Erika"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-center">Erika Adelaida Peñuela Vega</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/fernando.png"
                  alt="Angela"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[120px] h-[120px] object-cover"
                />
                <p class="text-center">Fernando Rodríguez Moreno</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/German Eduardo Torres Morales.jpg"
                  alt="Angela"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[120px] h-[120px] object-cover"
                />
                <p class="text-center">German Eduardo Torres Morales</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="my-5 text-center font-bold">
              Representantes del trabajador
            </p>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3">
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/carolina-angulo.jpg"
                  alt="carolina angulo"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />

                <p class="text-center">Carolina Angulo Ospina</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal-Secretaria CCL</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/maria-camila-gongora.png"
                  alt="Maria G"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-center">María Kamila Góngora</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Principal</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/nohora-patricia.png"
                  alt="Nohora"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-center">Nohora Patricia Quintero Cáceres</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <img
                  src="img/fotos/Paula-Andrea.png"
                  alt="Paula"
                  width="100"
                  height="100"
                  class="block mx-auto w-[130px] h-[130px] object-cover mb-5 rounded-full"
                />
                <p class="text-center">Paula Andrea León Peraza</p>
                <p class="text-center text-sm">Suplente</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <footer
      class="bg-azul-humboldt py-10 border-t-4 border-yellow-500 mt-5 absolute w-full"
      data-astro-cid-lptyvqux
    >
      <div class="max-w-[90%] mx-auto" data-astro-cid-lptyvqux>
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 justify-items-stretch"
          data-astro-cid-lptyvqux
        >
          <div data-astro-cid-lptyvqux>
            <div
